so that the most common words are on top here.

00:27:20.400 --> 00:27:23.319
So when we adopt tidy data principles

00:27:23.319 --> 00:27:25.719
and how we store our text,

00:27:25.719 --> 00:27:30.719
we are able to use very well-exercised,

00:27:33.119 --> 00:27:35.959
well-documented tools from the Tidyverse ecosystem

00:27:35.959 --> 00:27:39.640
to then be able to analyze the text that we have.

00:27:39.640 --> 00:27:43.400
So the only part here so far that is from tidy text

00:27:43.400 --> 00:27:45.079
is that unnest tokens.

