So now this tells us the top ten words for TFIDF for these three documents.

00:45:55.053 --> 00:46:00.973
So we see the Don Quixote words, panza, Dulcinea, Rocinante.

00:46:00.973 --> 00:46:05.892
You know, we hear� we see� so I was less familiar with these books before I was, like,

00:46:05.892 --> 00:46:06.892
looking for them for this talk.

00:46:06.892 --> 00:46:11.252
But I was like, oh, cool, this one has Gauchos and poems.

