Those are called engrams.

00:50:49.673 --> 00:50:52.252
So a word is a one-gram.

00:50:52.252 --> 00:50:56.413
A set of two words is a bigram or a two-gram.

00:50:56.413 --> 00:51:00.612
A set of three words is a trigram or a three-gram.

00:51:00.612 --> 00:51:03.492
So we've got� you probably still have this.

