So what were the things that come after he and what are the things that come after she?

00:55:30.752 --> 00:55:36.752
And then looked at the log odds here to say what comes� what is more likely to come

00:55:36.752 --> 00:55:40.793
after he and what is more likely to come after she?

00:55:40.793 --> 00:55:41.913
So let's look here.

00:55:41.913 --> 00:55:44.793
So we see she remembered.

00:55:44.793 --> 00:55:45.793
