It's another flavor.

01:23:26.079 --> 01:23:30.660
Buttery, tangy, mild, nutty, sweet, and then acidic.

01:23:30.660 --> 01:23:35.339
So these are the kinds of words that are in the descriptions of the flavors of the

01:23:35.339 --> 01:23:37.099
cheeses here.

01:23:37.099 --> 01:23:43.939
So if you are working along in the Posit cloud, you can, you can download the data and then

