Okay.

01:29:38.719 --> 01:29:41.540
So time for some cheesy embeddings.

01:29:41.540 --> 01:29:44.260
So we take...

01:29:44.260 --> 01:29:46.479
We have those cheeses.

01:29:46.479 --> 01:29:48.760
We have that cheeses data set.

01:29:48.760 --> 01:29:51.559
And we are going to take the flavor.

01:29:51.559 --> 01:29:53.079
The flavor column.

01:29:53.079 --> 01:29:57.760
Remember it was like milky, sweet, creamy.

01:29:57.760 --> 01:30:01.120
And so we are going to take out the columns...

01:30:01.120 --> 01:30:02.120
