So let's say I'm interested in Manchego.

01:34:35.339 --> 01:34:37.180
So Manchego is here.

01:34:37.180 --> 01:34:38.380
It's from Spain.

01:34:38.380 --> 01:34:44.900
And the flavor in this dataset for Manchego is buttery and nutty.

