That sounds about right to me.

01:34:46.339 --> 01:34:48.540
I think that sounds like Manchego to me.

01:34:48.540 --> 01:34:49.540
So let's say I start...

01:34:49.540 --> 01:34:50.540
I'm like...

01:34:50.540 --> 01:34:51.540
Okay.

01:34:51.540 --> 01:34:52.540
I want to know about Manchego.

01:34:52.540 --> 01:34:53.540
What...

01:34:53.540 --> 01:34:55.939
Oh, maybe I want to know...

